name: The stolen objkt of the Gnono #2
description:
This is a tutorial for all the hispanic speakers who wants to show us their art on this platform. 
(And is also the thing which the Gnono stole).
The goal of this work is to help people who are takin their first steps in HEN and promote people to continue creating art. 
Don't forger this important fact: If you aren't an artist but you want to make money on this platform, you don't have to upload content, you can buy works from other artist and resell them. 
Keep in mind what is mentioned at this work, because this can be useful to the new ones. It's relly important to the HEN community to continue to work in a correct way and following the HEN's purpouse: still being a plataform to share art.
